  title: Action Minis | Free Demo
  sections:
  - heading: 🔍 About
    text: "Thank you for downloading the Action Minis | Free Demo asset.
\n\nThis lowpoly character is part of the 'Mini Simple Characters' series and serves as a demo base to test compatibility and workflow before purchasing other characters or packs derived from this basemesh."
    linkText: 
    url: 
  - heading: 🧩 Modular System
    text: "Mix and match multiple parts to generate character variations.
\n\nPerfect for:
\n🔸Indie games
\n🔸Prototypes
\n🔸Full production projects
"
    linkText: 
    url: 
  - heading: ⚡ Performance Optimized
    text: "🔸Designed for real-time games
\n🔸Lowpoly geometry
\n🔸Single texture atlas
\n🔸Minimal draw calls
\n\n
\n✅ PC, Console and Mobile-friendly
\n✅ Lightweight scenes
\n✅ Fast rendering
"
    linkText: 
    url: 
  - heading: 🎨 Easy Color Customization
    text: "All models share a single texture atlas, reducing performance costs and simplifying texture management in your project.
\nAdjust texture offsets to create new color variations."
    linkText: 
    url: 
  - heading: 🖼️ Textures
    text: "- Diffuse / Albedo: 256px (.png)\n
\n✅Fast performance
\n✅Clean project structure
\n✅Easy color control
\n\n
⚠️ *Some models include multiple material slots (Primary, Secondary, Tertiary, etc).
\nCheck: Inspector → Skinned Mesh Renderer → Materials"
    linkText: 
    url: 
  - heading: 📐 Models & Polycount
    text: "- Total | 5.1k Tris\n\n- arms | 1728 Tris\n- chest | 184 Tris\n- head | 632 Tris\n- legs | 2144 Tris\n- nose | 40 Tris\n- pelvis | 192 Tris\n- torso | 192 Tris"
    linkText: 
    url: 
  - heading: 😊 Blendshapes
    text:  "❌ *This model has no Blendshapes included."
    linkText:
    url:
  - heading: 🕹️ Animations
    text:  "-Idle\n-Walk\n-Run\n-Jump\n-Loose\n
\n✅ Humanoid Rig (Mecanim Ready)
\n✅ Fully rigged and skinned

\n⚠️ *You can use <Generic> rig for custom animations or <Humanoid> to use retarget/mocap animations"
    linkText:
    url:
  - heading: 🧩 Modular Design
    text:  "This character is designed to be modular, making it easy to create a variety of combinations, allowing you to quickly create unique characters with maximum flexibility."
    linkText:
    url:
  - heading: ⭐ Key Features
    text:  "
🔸Modular character workflow\n
🔸Clean lowpoly stylized design\n
🔸Game-ready and optimized assets\n
🔸Mobile-ready performance\n
🔸Easy color variation workflow\n
🔸Cross-engine compatibility\n
🔸Production-friendly pipeline
"
    linkText:
    url:
  - heading: 🚀 Save Time. Ship Faster.
    text:  "Go from idea to playable character in minutes.
\nBuilt for developers who value speed, flexibility and performance."
    linkText:
  - heading:
    text:  "💚 Each asset has been carefully crafted to add a unique touch to your game project!"
    linkText:
    url:
